| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5557 — Recovery Inhibition (everest)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 24dc0c08-bfb3-535e-9f3a-bc7f69f4ff12"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
